data.description: What a great way to enjoy the community of April Sound! Custom built home right on the golf course! Lots of windows for natural light to filter in. Covered and enclosed back patio to relax and watch the golfers go by as you sip on your favorite beverage. Primary bedroom has huge walk in closet, jetted tub, and separate shower. Fourth bedroom can be used as a home office. Stunning fireplace with built-ins in the family room. Kitchen has an island with an electric cooktop but can easily be converted back to a gas cooktop. Great opportunity to move to this lakefront community!
